  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nBig issue. If you mention or reply to someone, that person will **not** receive that before they restart the app.\r\n\r\nSomething is broken with how we handle the signal.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Have both apps open\r\n2. send a mention or reply to account B\r\n3. account B doesn't receive it. They will only see it if they restart\r\n\r\n[Screencast 2023-02-20 13:43:48mention.webm](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/11926403/220180251-fdeaebed-590f-4573-b260-f6757503b34a.webm)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: master `c23f4e173e22e468f32a46322da004e84f844106`\r\n- Operating System: Ubuntu 20\r\n\r\n",
